DESCRIPTION:Stephanie Gailing\, Cloud Room's in-house Astrologer\, is offer
	ing Cloud Room Members complimentary 1-on-1 astrology readings and insight
	s via zoom! With over 20 years of professional experience\, Stephanie Gail
	ing weaves together astrological insights\, compassion-based coaching\, an
	d family constellations to provide her clients with stellar life guidance.
	 The author of seven books on wellness and astrology\, Stephanie is also t
	he co-host of the So Divine! Podcast. Her work has been featured in Vogue\
	, MindBodyGreen\, Well \\+ Good\, New Day Northwest\, The Seattle Times\, 
	and other outlets. Make sure to sign up for a 15 minute session while they
	're available.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/wellness-w
	ednesday-astrology-readings-with-stephanie-gailing/18061648/2026-03-11T00\
	n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
