UID:9gPm2X_NH-adxm2PUG8ek
SUMMARY:Golden Ear Awards Party
DTSTAMP:20260306T004548Z
DTSTART:20260317T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Concert 7:00PM Doors 5:30PM Tickets: Sliding Scale $10/ $15/ $2
	0 \\+ processing fees Come join the party as we celebrate the outstanding 
	achievements of Seattle jazz artists in 2025. The ceremony recognizes both
	 emerging talent and Seattle veterans from all jazz genres. Special awards
	 are also presented to people or groups that have made extraordinary contr
	ibutions in 2025\, perhaps through a remarkable presentation\, support to 
	fellow artists\, or new initiatives in education or collaboration. Helping
	 us celebrate is a local ensemble TBD. The Golden Ear Awards Ceremony will
	 be hosted by a local musician ABOUT GOLDEN EAR AWARDS Earshot Jazz initia
	ted the Golden Ear Awards in 1990 to recognize the accomplishments of Seat
	tle jazz artists over the previous year\, and to induct significant member
	s of the jazz community into the local Jazz Hall of Fame. Over the years\,
	 the award categories have shifted slightly\, but the essence of the proce
	ss has remained the same. Nominations accepted year round via email\; nomi
	nations can also be cast through the following form: https://forms.gle/daX
	EM7arSWTrV6XL6 The official ballot comes out every February Ceremony and c
	oncert in March — This year’s Golden Ear Awards Party is scheduled for Mon
	day\, March 16 at The Royal Room.” \\*\\*Please note: tickets do not guara
	ntee seats. Seats must be arranged separately with The Royal Room: The Roy
	al Room accepts dinner reservations. Please reserve here: https://theroyal
	roomseattle.com/reservations\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/deta
	ils/golden-ear-awards-party/18228352/2026-03-16T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts
	 & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/golden-ear-awards-party/1
	8228352/2026-03-16T00
LOCATION:The Royal Room\, 5000 Rainier Ave South\, Seattle\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-arts
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
